      "writtenOn": "2017-10-04T05:33:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I might trim this down to something less fancy, since you want to be certain that it doesn\u0027t load a DLL. I don\u0027t see anything that would cause it to, but I\u0027m vaguely thinking of the CRT loading a DLL in a different locale or something.\n\nThe benefit of the file:line, path split, % formatting over simply \"puts(\"Error\"); TerminateProcess();\" seems pretty minor here too.\n\n(Only a thought, feel free to leave it as-is if that seems unlikely to you.)",
